_sText:
I have had this map laying around for a few years, and thought it was a shame that I never got around to completely finish it, so I figured I wanted to upload it as is. As it is now, it is to be considered beta stage, because it could have been further optimised. Hope you enjoy it anyways :) - I know I had loads of fun making it! :D - - - - - - - - - De_Metropolitan is my very first map (not a typical first map, I know).

**The map features:**
42 spawnpoints
light switches
camera + monitor
Elevator
Metro
enterable Bar, apartment complex and a house
Custom textures
custom models
soundscapes
2 bombsites
Loads and loads of love :'D <3
